title: Berner and Ampachino - Traffic Vol. 2
description:
Traffic, Vol. 2: Trains, Planes & Automobiles album for sale by Berner & Ampichino was released Nov 16, 2010 on the Double F label. Berner and Ampichino collaborate on Traffic 2, the second CD which takes the listener into the high stakes and high risk world of the drug trade. Audio Mixer: Randy Biddle. Traffic, Vol. 2: Trains, Planes & Automobiles CD music contains a single disc with 19 songs.
